{"tid":1458222,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【整合】各種風向撚及相應對策，唔好再錯傷自己人！","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:06:45.000Z","uid":204307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e821d2aef3733aad98fb4c6d25e831c12596d59","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"重開<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458026/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458026/page/1</a><br />\n頭先標題改得衰無咩人見到 希望今次work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日機場散水事件，資訊極度混雜，成個連登無論係熱門定係最新，唔係一堆pk真鬼post，就係一堆責罵、捉鬼post洗版，睇大家互屌嘅氣氛簡直就係14年翻版。<br />\n我盡量整合佐一下今晚各種帶風向言論嘅類型，希望大家一齊集思廣益，思考對策，提供建議改善我地嘅討論。緊記，對家最犀利就係分化，我地都要進化。<br />\n<br />\n1. 真三毛鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般只有文字轉述重大資訊，有時加句已fc就當source。言論中往往有隱藏嘅惡意，將矛頭指去某一立場嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n對策：純文字/證據不足post，全部人用不推文功能問source，直至有proof，期間可以善用起底功能，有時自己友會做標題黨，自問自己處於安全環境嘅，就幫手click入去睇睇d posts有無問題，確實身份後block。<br />\n<br />\n2. 凡事block/鬧佐先嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近每個人壓力都好大，見到可疑言論躁底就二話不說block，甚至以人身攻擊（例如針對對方P牌）作為佢哋滅聲嘅理據，但佢哋往往無惡意，純粹因為擔心情況惡化先咁激動。<br />\n<br />\n對策：覺得唔可靠嘅post，用不推文功能，提出引導性問題要求clarify言論，切勿一開波就屌人，以避免誤傷自己人，或filter佐有用意見。<br />\n<br />\n3. 信任親友，覺得唔洗fc佢哋說話嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多來自親友嘅一手資訊，我地都會先入其中當真先，最後可能無惡意地炒車被其他兄弟當鬼block。<br />\n<br />\n對策：出post前問親友，source係咩？出post後發現炒車，請去站務台要求連仔del走錯誤資訊嘅post，並向各位巴絲道歉澄清。<br />\n<br />\n4. 擔心親友安危，將憂慮直接放上黎嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如訊號唔好，打電話無人聽，或者睇直播見到疑似自己朋友出事嘅危險情況，為爭分奪秒，未fc就發放表示有義士需要幫助嘅言論。<br />\n<br />\n對策：每位義士，請向自己信任嘅至少兩個熟人提供自己嘅緊急聯絡方法，例如留底自己家人電話俾佢哋，提供多幾個途徑，俾關心你地嘅人fc你嘅現況。可以download依家免費開放俾香港人嘅parachute app，以作求救及錄影證據，詳情search app store。<br />\n<br />\n5. 出於好心誤shared連登上面錯誤資訊上ig/fb，其他人又當ig/fb係source，share翻上連登當fact check佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對策：除非有任何有力證據/資訊根本無咩辦法fc，請各位手足唔好盲目相信各媒介發放嘅資料，另外可以facebook inbox你地嘅懷疑俾做緊直播嘅新聞page，由前線記者做fact check，例如立場（811由於各地兵荒馬亂，立場inbox秒seen讀者有圖嘅訊息）。<br />\n<br />\n6.post太長，直接睇最後一頁就當係結論嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對策：善用圖片功能，睇佐有圖嘅留言先，再利用相關回覆自行整理重點，有時間的話可以打埋出黎俾大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n整合佐好耐，好努力思考過先出post，希望大家每次出現異常情況嗰陣，都可以整理心情，總結當日奇怪嘅地方，開放俾大家討論。<br />\n小妹不才，希望大家幫手推post之餘，都提出更多建議，大家分工合作，見招拆招。<br />\n<br />\n新官上任，我地都要學下點樣進步，我愛各位戰友，請求各位珍惜自己人，香港唔知仲有無下一個5年了，光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"70702d2b5525dd89a92707509f8073e3946fc4f7","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"重開直接copy搞到d顏色無曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望唔影響閱讀<br />\n自推"},{"pid":"91b66c406bd35d813a9ae24546762576301e6ef7","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:23:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"626a89dea2e9471c003562446b5c2fe727f9e4b0","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9b00acb34473b4019d571d312d0b06ac3496174a","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2bb234af09316035e90f136a0908072019480243","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"e93f05990c345725aef787ae0a759da18b8e6d6a","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d0597f26f742c4474a4aa0ed8c45bc7dd3257383","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"ca1a0a867d1a3039e6e7123d764cb3811d065295","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"82e13d224c5c2f4742c48850f6dbba74d188e126","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"907f13d8a8fa3c70a80bdb7657c856e4c7976778","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"035cee971e63c0fbe728ae94f3fdc9ea381cd2ba","tid":1458222,"uid":204307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"10 sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c827d2dd54f28164b7d4d10653d657812e67bea","tid":1458222,"uid":280436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"【散 定唔散 都係政府個局入面】<br />\n<br />\n政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">操縱緊我地嘅言論</span></span>去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">分化</span></span>勇武同和理非<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果散</span> <br />\n就發表大量<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌撚散水狗</span></span></span>嘅言論<br />\n馬後砲<br />\n指責班合理擔心安全嘅和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">be water</span></span>係大家一直以來重視嘅嘢<br />\n根本勇武唔會怪責<br />\n可見係政府故意引起割席<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">唔散</span><br />\n警察真係做嘢<br />\n就會湧現和理非怪責勇武嘅言論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一切 都係政府設下嘅套路！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日真係有取消/延誤航班 <br />\n警察真係有佈防 而且有機會用得到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但真正目的並非實質行動<br />\n而係分化大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近安插臥底係前線同樣<br />\n都有一層目的係為左令尼場運動嘅參與者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自行瓦解</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大量網軍混入連登，Facebook，telegram<br />\n散播謠言<br />\n令大家<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑</span>盟友嘅可信性<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">互相猜忌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家千奇唔好中政府嘅詭計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">謹記 不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅陰濕招數 我地只要團結 一定搵到方法破解"},{"pid":"aaaf75acb0ab4e4c15df490cb9c861799499b0fe","tid":1458222,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:54:30.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手支持廣獨，將革命思想傳入中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehx7Ac4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fehx7Ac4.jpg&h=3f367942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=fb59b157\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV</a>"},{"pid":"2198bcec9ef8026e5af78dd9c0e417a07409b068","tid":1458222,"uid":277328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"我推"},{"pid":"53ff4f3fb17e5eb5a5ee29a41aa4f6321097b1d3","tid":1458222,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"721"}]}